title: The Queen's Gambit - You're Gloating (Piano Cover)
description:
This is my second arrangement from this wonderful soundtrack. I got a few more I'd want to do, including The Final Game and Sygrayem (Let's Play). I'm starting my end of semester here so I'll do them as fast as possible.
Again, please leave suggestions in the comments!
I do all my arrangements by ear so no sheets sorry.
Thanks a lot for watching
